{"tid":1985060,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"（物理治療入) Sacroiliac joint 骶髂關節根治方法","createTime":"2020-04-23T01:48:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T17:25:10.000Z","uid":21361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"be9598179ae3a540dbcc7d6f8d1543c393a22f2b","tid":1985060,"uid":21361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T01:48:31.000Z","msg":"一年前做deadlift  下背右邊chok左一下  右邊屎忽近腰位一直痛  之後無做gym半年諗住好返  點知都係keep住麻麻痺痺咁痛 <br />\n<br />\n大概紅色點個啲位置 (尾龍骨位 hip位同hamstring)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LjPObgQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLjPObgQ.png&h=7a941a3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f4F9Fad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff4F9Fad.png&h=9b98d428&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇過6 7次中醫 物理治療做過針灸同推拿  係舒服左啲  但之後都係有啲麻麻痺痺痛 <br />\n<br />\n之後轉睇左第2個physio 話我應該係si joint整親  教左我一啲stretching 同訓練動作 keep住練左2個星期都好似無咩用  想問下有咩方法可以斷尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad2d4fa3352f650fafcc8f26fba9c7e98a75aae","tid":1985060,"uid":21361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T04:01:49.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a81925f8d98967cc2a586de6966ca37dcc10fb","tid":1985060,"uid":136327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T04:23:42.000Z","msg":"有冇check過是咪spondylolisthesis"},{"pid":"6c668d878f55691a39feca6a3bbcdcc058f99c52","tid":1985060,"uid":50180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T04:54:49.000Z","msg":"就咁聽你文字表達<br />\n判斷唔到係咪真係si joint problem"},{"pid":"494aed86006a7ca243ccc95fb5f7fc478a35e3d0","tid":1985060,"uid":199688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T12:16:28.000Z","msg":"可能係Sciatica，即係坐骨神經痛。可以試下做直腿抬高測驗，即係個人平瞓，之後抬高右腳，要keep住knee伸直。如果可以重現個痛，你就應該有sciatica. 你可以試下呢個test先"},{"pid":"fbcce53094a651875b340bfeacc03d0f24f19f72","tid":1985060,"uid":21361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11a81925f8d98967cc2a586de6966ca37dcc10fb","tid":1985060,"uid":136327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T04:23:42.000Z","msg":"有冇check過是咪spondylolisthesis"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:06:19.000Z","msg":"姐係椎間盤突出？ 我係向左扭腰既時候feel 到右邊下腰拉住咁，平時行，坐，跑都無咩感覺"},{"pid":"b0ae90f9893272cdd35a1ea95526cfb3c2b74036","tid":1985060,"uid":21361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"494aed86006a7ca243ccc95fb5f7fc478a35e3d0","tid":1985060,"uid":199688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T12:16:28.000Z","msg":"可能係Sciatica，即係坐骨神經痛。可以試下做直腿抬高測驗，即係個人平瞓，之後抬高右腳，要keep住knee伸直。如果可以重現個痛，你就應該有sciatica. 你可以試下呢個test先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:12:25.000Z","msg":"我做呢個動作無痛 平時坐都無乜點痛  係向左扭既時候有啲隱隱痛"},{"pid":"d4fea1284a290dff5612220404c52b1683164737","tid":1985060,"uid":155654,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:12:12.000Z","msg":"除左stretch之外要用野碌，同埋用硬身既波<br />\n<br />\n有機會你唔識stretch, OR stretch得唔應<br />\n按又按得唔好<br />\nstretch都有好多款動作去搵你最唔舒服個位出黎<br />\n你去睇d physio可能睇幾十次都未斷尾<br />\n搵有經驗既教練教會好D , 同時都執番好Deadlift個動作"},{"pid":"eb468d365b435d1fa4bb4bf0dd9d285750e4c944","tid":1985060,"uid":29567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T02:55:21.000Z","msg":"如果係si joint問題<br />\n你要expect康復時間比較長<br />\n因為呢個關節周圍嘅組織係一堆韌帶<br />\n而韌帶復原，視乎損傷程度同範圍，多則需要2個月嘅時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以樓主未必可以喺短時間內復原<br />\n<br />\n但如果唔係si joint嘅問題，而係上面回覆所講嘅問題<br />\n咁你嘅治療方向可能錯咗<br />\n但你會信親身同你驗查嘅物理治療師定係網上嘅猜測？<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f1c2032c64e67296d43822079108ca7f5a32cd","tid":1985060,"uid":21361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4fea1284a290dff5612220404c52b16